ack.title: Acknowledgments
ack.p: The authors wish to thank the veterinarians who have contributed to this work by collecting samples; they also thank all the staff of the Regional Veterinary Laboratory of El-Tarf (LVR el-Tarf) and more specifically the Director of LVR El-Tarf: Mr. Houner and the staff of the food hygiene service. The research was funded by the first author (Narimene Mansouri) and the Laboratory Research of Epidemiologic monitoring, Health, Production, Reproduction, Experimentation and Cellular Therapy of Domestic and Wild Animals, Department of Veterinary Medicine, University of Chadli Bendjedid, El-Tarf, Algeria.
